{"tid":1966820,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"本港多16人確診　一名男患者的女友曾到酒吧","createTime":"2020-04-10T12:36:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-10T13:26:47.000Z","uid":57677,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1181711129fab0fc23675c55eab84a79f079b700","tid":1966820,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T12:36:02.000Z","msg":"醫管局總行政經理何婉霞表示，上星期六確診感染新型冠狀病毒的46歲西九龍總區機動部隊警長，以及一名無長期病患的28歲加拿大留學生，是其中兩名危殆病人，兩人昨日開始氣促，含氧量轉差，需要插喉，以呼吸機協助呼吸。而一名到過美國及加拿大的75歲危殆女病人，今日情況轉差，需要使用人工肺。她在深切治療部已留院一段時間，要用呼吸機。醫管局現時有20多部人工肺儀器，局方設有專家小組，檢視人工肺的使用情況，由於只有約2%病人需要進入深切治療部，相信人工肺數量暫時足夠。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n何婉霞指，目前仍然留院的確診病人中，有15人危殆、9人嚴重，其餘情況穩定。而過去二十四小時再多16名病人康復出院，累計有309名病人已出院。"},{"pid":"c9a701dce8e819e38003c3d3bb0ffbcdc536f482","tid":1966820,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T12:39:55.000Z","msg":"回落啦"},{"pid":"eebca32338121bd95d7f8ec174d6282ce22990dc","tid":1966820,"uid":3302,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T12:40:27.000Z","msg":"頂綠帽大到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66f6626133ab86546123b803d4aa3524a4c49abe","tid":1966820,"uid":26333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eebca32338121bd95d7f8ec174d6282ce22990dc","tid":1966820,"uid":3302,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T12:40:27.000Z","msg":"頂綠帽大到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T12:41:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25fcd31e014328662eea93b3f38827cda6c7a2a8","tid":1966820,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T12:42:30.000Z","msg":"本港再多16人感染新型冠狀病毒，累計確診宗數增至989宗。新增患者包括10男6女，年齡由17至75歲，只有1人沒有外遊紀錄，是一名<span style=\"color: blue;\">28歲男子</span>，他的<span style=\"color: violet;\">女朋友</span>曾到過尖沙咀諾士佛臺的All Night Long酒吧。衛生防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君表示，可能出<span style=\"color: green;\">現二代傳播</span>。其餘15名新增患者，全部有外遊紀錄，當中8人是返港留學生。<br />\n<br />\n張竹君又指，未來的疫情發展，視乎人群是否有社交距離。她說今日見到街上有好多人，感到擔心，指如果大家放鬆了而聚集，出現隱性傳播，可能會有第二波爆發。"},{"pid":"99c7a09468563c4148a54ef4adbbcf5d04b62aa2","tid":1966820,"uid":89064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eebca32338121bd95d7f8ec174d6282ce22990dc","tid":1966820,"uid":3302,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T12:40:27.000Z","msg":"頂綠帽大到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T12:42:38.000Z","msg":"同果條女打過車輪/扑過野條陌生男都唔好得去邊，中招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79f222a2e80983006b37934520ce7402c26426d7","tid":1966820,"uid":315626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T12:43:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d4fa00293117daec0451cfe53c5e9ad74f835a3","tid":1966820,"uid":118120,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T12:44:09.000Z","msg":"個女友都算仆街,  俾綠帽人戴都算, <br />\n仲要俾埋武漢肺炎病毒人地<br />\n呢d 真係陀衰家"},{"pid":"c1601479e656088cc26048859f5fc9642f1bc9fd","tid":1966820,"uid":157261,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T12:44:37.000Z","msg":"綠完仲要中招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\